WEBVTT

00:01.480 --> 00:03.280
《越狱》前情回顾
Previously on Prison Break

00:03.290 --> 00:04.830
孩子 我对你没什么成见
I got nothing against you, kid.

00:04.840 --> 00:05.990
你要做什么?
What are you doing, man?

00:06.000 --> 00:09.280
但是子弹有
But they do.

00:10.480 --> 00:15.190
你们的好朋友曼彻告诉了我有关 搜寻韦斯特莫兰德藏款的计划
Your pal manche told me all about your little treasure hunt for Westmoreland's stash.

00:15.200 --> 00:17.020
我们出发去犹他州
We're going to Utah.

00:17.030 --> 00:17.390
傻瓜
Fooled you.

00:17.400 --> 00:19.890
把手放在背后
Hands behind your back.

00:19.900 --> 00:24.030
-你随意好了 -好的
-Make yourself at home. -Sure.

00:26.530 --> 00:28.770
你父亲接到了通白宫打来的电话
Your father got a call from the White House.

00:28.780 --> 00:30.150
撤销了你父亲的候选提名
They withdrew his nomination.

00:30.160 --> 00:33.180
根据他们的说法 你父亲的批准程序有些问题
According to them, his confirmation was going to be a problem.

00:33.190 --> 00:35.280
我爸爸不会自杀的
My father is not a suicidal man.

00:35.290 --> 00:37.430
唐克雷蒂州长不在我们计划之内
Governor Tancredi, not part of our plan.

00:37.440 --> 00:39.650
任何知道蛛丝马迹的人都不能放过
Anyone who knows anything has got to be dealt with.

00:39.660 --> 00:41.420
如果有人成了累赘  就干掉他们
If someone's a liability, they go.

00:41.430 --> 00:43.140
唐克雷蒂就是个累赘
Tancredi was becoming a liability.

00:43.150 --> 00:44.390
他女儿也是
So was his daughter.

00:44.400 --> 00:46.950
等等  什么?
Wait, what?

00:46.960 --> 00:48.190
布伦斯按计划将于
Burrows is scheduled to be released

00:48.200 --> 00:49.820
明日在其关押地亚利桑那州的
from the Klipton Detention Center in Kingman, Arizona

00:49.830 --> 00:52.450
克利普顿拘留中心被释放
tomorrow morning.

00:52.460 --> 00:56.190
LJ释放出来了 我要去接他
LJ is out there;I'm going to get him.

00:56.200 --> 00:58.990
保重
Take care.

00:59.000 --> 01:01.750
查尔斯 韦斯特莫兰德...
Charles Westmoreland...

01:01.760 --> 01:05.190
愿上帝保佑你  还有你的破麻袋
god bless you and your wrinkled old sack.

01:05.200 --> 01:06.420
全在这儿了
It's all here.

01:06.430 --> 01:08.090
苏克雷在哪?
Where's Sucre?

01:08.100 --> 01:09.390
放下包
Drop the bag.

01:09.400 --> 01:13.230
谁都不许走
No one's going anywhere.

01:23.030 --> 01:24.620
你他妈的在搞什么鬼?
What the hell are you doing, man?

01:24.630 --> 01:26.750
苏克雷 不论你想要什么
Sucre...whatever it is you want...

01:26.760 --> 01:29.690
我要钱  所有的钱
I want the money, all of it.

01:29.700 --> 01:31.020
什么  你要抢我们的钱?
What, are you robbing us?

01:31.030 --> 01:33.390
钱本来就不是你们的
The money was never yours to begin with.

01:33.400 --> 01:34.590
这只是一个交易
This is about business.

01:34.600 --> 01:36.850
500万美金值得我搏一记
$5 million worth of business.

01:36.860 --> 01:39.590
这就是我们共患难的结果?
So this is how it's going to go down, huh?

01:39.600 --> 01:43.100
我们共同经历了所有的事
After everything.

01:44.030 --> 01:45.620
贼就是江山易改本性难移
Once a thief, always a thief.

01:45.630 --> 01:46.990
你才意识到啊?
You just figuring that out?

01:47.000 --> 01:50.620
给我背包
The backpack.

01:50.630 --> 01:53.760
快!
Now!

01:55.930 --> 01:59.430
兄弟  别这么做
Don't do this, buddy.

01:59.690 --> 02:01.970
小子  你自己好好合计一下
Yo, take a look around you, papi.

02:01.980 --> 02:03.720
我们有三个人而你只孤身一人
It's three of us, it's one of you

02:03.730 --> 02:06.710
难道这笔帐你不会算 我们会一直追你到天涯海角
you are outnumbered, man, and we will come after you.

02:06.720 --> 02:08.210
兄弟  这可能是你能做的最后一件事了
It'll be the last thing you do, my brother.

02:08.220 --> 02:09.950
你打算把我们都打死?
What, are you going to shoot at all of us?

02:09.960 --> 02:13.460
也许不会
Probably not.

02:14.810 --> 02:16.830
但是我可以打死两个
but I will get two.

02:16.840 --> 02:18.540
现在...
Now...

02:18.550 --> 02:22.390
谁想成为那两个呢?
which two is it going to be?

02:22.400 --> 02:24.220
这就对了
That's what I thought.

02:24.230 --> 02:28.360
再见  朋友们
Adios, amigos.

02:33.500 --> 02:36.650
我真不敢相信
I don't believe this.

02:36.660 --> 02:39.790
我们历经艰险 好不容易光明就在眼前
We have come all this way and done all of this work.

02:39.800 --> 02:43.900
纹身小子  你们不还是好兄弟吗?
Thought you was compadres, tattoo?

02:44.460 --> 02:46.890
伙计们  那我们现在怎么办
so what are we going to do now, man?

02:46.900 --> 02:48.890
警察随时都会到
The police are going to be here any second.

02:48.900 --> 02:51.890
我绝不能容忍那傻大个带着
Ain't no way I'm letting that- that dunderpate

02:51.900 --> 02:53.720
五百万跑了…
ride off with five...

02:53.730 --> 02:57.730
你们自己决定吧
It's your choice.

03:02.560 --> 03:07.130
放心没什么事
It's all right.

03:09.960 --> 03:13.450
别担心  给你这个  然后...
all right, I'm going to give you this, and, uh...

03:13.460 --> 03:14.890
大约一个小时后你就可以
you should be able to cut yourself free

03:14.900 --> 03:18.700
割断绳子重获自由
in about an hour.

03:19.260 --> 03:20.590
伙计  你有什么计划?
So what's the plan, man?

03:20.600 --> 03:22.220
你想做什么都行
Well, you can do what you want.

03:22.230 --> 03:24.820
我让帝博格那个变态逃过一次
I let that psychopath t-bag loose once.

03:24.830 --> 03:27.020
我不会再让他逃脱惩罚
I'm not going to do it again.

03:27.030 --> 03:31.860
警察来的时候给他们留个小礼物
Make a nice little present for the police when they get here.

03:34.830 --> 03:40.400
他哪儿去了?
Where is he?

03:42.360 --> 03:43.850
我不知道
I don't know

03:43.860 --> 03:46.950
伙计  我也该…我也该走了
man, look, I got to, I got to go.

03:46.960 --> 03:50.460
好运
Uh, good luck.

03:59.830 --> 04:04.230
他们会抓到你的
They're going to get you.

04:18.530 --> 04:20.050
唐克雷蒂小姐
Ms.Tancredi.

04:20.060 --> 04:21.490
我并不想吓到你
I didn't mean to startle you.

04:21.500 --> 04:23.220
该死的  你在我屋里干什么?
What the hell are you doing in my house?

04:23.230 --> 04:24.990
没什么好怕的
No reason to be frightened.

04:25.000 --> 04:28.790
我以前和你父亲一起工作
I used to work with your father.

04:28.800 --> 04:32.430
对你父亲的死我深表遗憾
I'm so sorry for your loss.

04:38.330 --> 04:43.130
我父亲不是自杀的
My father didn't commit suicide.

04:43.700 --> 04:46.120
你在干什么?
What are you doing?

04:46.130 --> 04:47.590
让人确信我没像之前那样吸毒
Making sure it doesn't look like I did!

04:47.600 --> 04:48.850
如果州长自杀的当天
People will ask questions

04:48.860 --> 04:51.120
他女儿也被发现死于非命 现场还留有搏斗痕迹
if the day the governor was found killing himself

04:51.130 --> 04:55.790
那么人们肯定会产生疑惑
his daughter is found dead in what looks like a struggle.

04:55.800 --> 04:58.790
那么  好吧
Well, then.

04:58.800 --> 05:01.120
如果他们找不到她呢?
What if they don't find her?

05:01.130 --> 05:04.390
很明显州长的女儿为了避免牢狱之灾
In an apparent attempt to avoid jail time,

05:04.400 --> 05:08.720
在保释中逃走并消失了
the governor's daughter skips bail and disappears.

05:08.730 --> 05:10.920
我们在说你最后的几分钟  唐克雷蒂小姐
We're talking about your last minutes, Ms.Tancredi.

05:10.930 --> 05:12.490
别这么做
Please don't do this.

05:12.500 --> 05:14.520
桌子上的东西非常昂贵
That stuff on that table is premium.

05:14.530 --> 05:15.790
A等品
It's grade "A".

05:15.800 --> 05:17.250
帮你自己个忙
Do yourself a favor

05:17.260 --> 05:18.520
出去享受一下
go out on a high.

05:18.530 --> 05:19.920
我求求你
Look, I'm begging you here.

05:19.930 --> 05:23.730
最后的盛宴
One last ride.

05:24.460 --> 05:27.830
哦  妈的!
Oh, god!

06:24.330 --> 06:28.230
"再见 朋友们"嗯?
Adios, amigos, huh?

06:30.060 --> 06:32.550
怎么?  演过头了?
What? Too much?

06:32.560 --> 06:36.600
干得漂亮
You were great.

06:39.600 --> 06:41.790
老兄  这东西真他妈的重
this thing is freaking heavy, dude.

06:41.800 --> 06:43.120
分了它就不会这么重了
Won't be so bad after we split it up.

06:43.130 --> 06:45.650
3个人分  我  你  还有林肯
Three ways: Me, you and Linc.

06:45.660 --> 06:47.220
是4个
Four.

06:47.230 --> 06:49.490
我们得分给查尔斯的女儿一部分
We're going to send a share to Charles's daughter

06:49.500 --> 06:50.820
并捎上他父亲给她的爱
with her father's love

06:50.830 --> 06:51.890
正如之前承诺的那样
just like we promised.

06:51.900 --> 06:54.220
富兰克林怎么办?
What about C-Note?

06:54.230 --> 06:55.420
我总觉得整件事有点不太好
I feel kind of bad about the whole thing.

06:55.430 --> 06:56.950
我们没法知道该不该信任他
There's no way to know if we could trust him.

06:56.960 --> 06:58.190
等我们到了巴拿马
Once we get down to Panama

06:58.200 --> 06:59.350
我们再往他家里汇些钱吧
we'll send something up to his family

06:59.360 --> 07:00.520
确保他能过好点
make sure he's taken care of.

07:00.530 --> 07:04.990
500万美金
Five million dollars.

07:05.000 --> 07:09.290
我真不敢相信  我就要成为...
I can't believe I'm going to be...

07:09.300 --> 07:13.320
见鬼钱到哪去了?
where the hell is the money?

07:13.330 --> 07:17.600
见鬼钱到哪去了?
Where the hell is the money?

07:43.530 --> 07:48.130
背包...快!
The backpack...Now!

07:58.770 --> 08:01.880
出售汽车
for sale by owner

08:56.160 --> 08:58.220
布伦斯先生?
Mr.Burrows?

08:58.230 --> 09:00.020
恭喜你出来!
Merry christmas from the state.

09:00.580 --> 09:04.440
这张清单上有居住及招工信息可供选择
Here's a list of options available to you.

09:04.450 --> 09:09.080
有些公司更愿意雇一些出狱的人
Places to stay, businesses that are more open to hiring men out of the correctional system.

09:20.780 --> 09:22.670
对你即将面对的未来有什么问题吗?
Any questions you might have about your immediate future?

09:22.680 --> 09:26.150
没有
No.

09:29.210 --> 09:31.900
好吧  这上面的电话是免费的
Well, the number on there is toll-free.

09:31.910 --> 09:34.700
遇到任何问题随时都可以打这个电话
If you encounter any problems, you can call there 24-7.

09:34.710 --> 09:36.900
-谢谢  -等下
-Thanks. Wait a second.

09:36.910 --> 09:38.140
你知道吗?
You know what?

09:38.150 --> 09:39.800
为什么不告诉我你要去哪呢？
Why don't you tell me where you need to go

09:39.810 --> 09:44.010
我可以载你过去
and I'll make sure you get there.

09:45.250 --> 09:47.390
行了  我没事的
You know, I think I'll be all right.

09:47.400 --> 09:48.860
你确定?
You sure?

09:48.870 --> 09:52.380
是的  谢谢
Yeah.Thank you.

10:00.150 --> 10:02.740
孩子没上钩
Kid didn't bite.

10:02.750 --> 10:03.800
他步行的
He's on foot

10:03.810 --> 10:04.870
好吧
All right.

10:04.880 --> 10:06.970
派人跟着他
Have your men follow.

10:06.980 --> 10:08.240
记住我们要找的是他爸爸
Remember, it's the father we want.

10:10.250 --> 10:12.270
我们不可以回去
We can't go back.

10:12.280 --> 10:14.040
你说过  没钱我们就完蛋了
You said it, without the money, we're screwed.

10:14.050 --> 10:15.810
我们不能...让我想想
We can't... just let me think.

10:15.820 --> 10:17.470
或许还在...让我想想!让我想想!
- Maybe it's still back... - Just let me think! Let me think.

10:17.480 --> 10:19.540
或许钱还在屋里
Maybe it's still back at the house.

10:19.550 --> 10:21.140
钱不在屋里
The money's not back at the house

10:21.150 --> 10:25.500
除非帝博格还在那儿
unless T-Bag is

10:25.510 --> 10:28.000
他一定是把背包换了
He must've switched the packs.

10:28.010 --> 10:29.440
那...?
wh-what do we do...

10:29.450 --> 10:31.140
我们现在怎么办?
what do we do now?

10:31.150 --> 10:33.400
这里还有5千美元
We still got the five grand we took

10:33.410 --> 10:35.640
装钱的时候留下的
when we pocketed the money.

10:35.650 --> 10:38.170
没有五百万那么多
It's not gonna be five million

10:38.180 --> 10:39.900
但也足够我们到要去的地方了
but it might be enough to get us where we're going.

10:39.910 --> 10:41.640
各单位注意
All units be advised.

10:41.650 --> 10:44.770
福克斯河监狱的逃犯被确定
Escaped convicts from fox river have been positively ID'd

10:44.780 --> 10:46.800
在蒙特里路1131号
at 1131 monterey lane

10:46.810 --> 10:48.470
我们已经出动警犬进行搜索
We have dogs being dispatched to the location.

10:48.480 --> 10:51.770
进出镇的每条路都封锁起来
I want every road in or out of town blocked off.

10:51.780 --> 10:53.940
不管是汽车  火车  还是走路
I don't care if it's on wheels, rails or hooves.

10:53.950 --> 10:57.770
都拦下来  仔细检查
I want it stopped and searched.

10:57.780 --> 10:59.740
我记得你说过我们始终快他们一程
I thought you said we would have a head start.

10:59.750 --> 11:01.140
是那枪声暴露了
It was the gunshot, buddy.

11:01.150 --> 11:02.870
一定是被某个邻居听到了
One of the neighbors must've heard.

11:02.880 --> 11:04.440
那东西能开多快?
How fast can that thing go?

11:04.450 --> 11:05.540
不知道
I don't know.

11:05.550 --> 11:08.710
我们俩的话  或许...
Both of us, it could probably...

11:10.780 --> 11:14.640
我们不可能从马路走了
we're never gonna get out of here on the roads.

11:14.650 --> 11:17.530
我们得想其他途径
We need to find another way.

11:17.540 --> 11:20.840
伊利诺州  芝加哥   FBI办公室
Chicago, Illinois FBI Filed Office

11:20.850 --> 11:23.370
他在你办公室了
He's in your office.

11:23.380 --> 11:25.140
谁让他进来的?
Who let him in?

11:25.150 --> 11:26.770
真难以置信这个节骨眼上把我招回
I can't believe they're calling me back here

11:26.780 --> 11:28.000
那些逃犯都还逍遥法外
when my escapees are out there.

11:28.010 --> 11:29.570
我想知道这个家伙是谁
I want to know who this guy is.

11:29.580 --> 11:33.140
他说他叫萨林斯
Said his name was Sullins.

11:33.150 --> 11:34.340
狗娘养的
Son of a bitch.

11:34.350 --> 11:40.910
逃犯这边有什么进展马上通知我
Let me know if anything breaks on the convicts.

11:42.180 --> 11:43.140
亚历克斯
Alex.

11:43.150 --> 11:44.170
谢谢你能来
Thanks for coming in.

11:44.180 --> 11:45.600
你能告诉我为什么内务部
You want to tell me why internal affairs is pulling me out of the field

11:45.610 --> 11:47.700
在我追踪逃犯中途招回我?
in the middle of a manhunt?

11:47.710 --> 11:50.440
好久没和你坐下来谈谈了吧?
It's been a while since we've had a sit-down, hasn't it?

11:50.450 --> 11:52.200
自从肖逃走以来都没有过吧?
Not since the shales escape, am I right?

11:52.210 --> 11:53.770
是的  到底怎么样  理查德?
Yeah, yeah. What's going on, Richard?

11:53.780 --> 11:55.270
好吧...
Well...

11:55.280 --> 11:59.650
这正是我来这的目的
that's precisely what I'm here to find out.

12:00.410 --> 12:05.110
在我完事前你不能出去
And you're not getting out of here until I do.

12:05.960 --> 12:09.500
怀俄明州  莱曼
Lyman, Wyoming

12:09.510 --> 12:11.900
哦  天哪
Oh, my god.

12:11.910 --> 12:16.010
人类的文明
Civilization.

12:25.950 --> 12:29.470
要点什么?
What can I get for you boys?

12:29.480 --> 12:30.270
你看呢
You tell me.

12:30.280 --> 12:32.900
两杯水吧
Two waters, then.

12:32.910 --> 12:36.470
知道你是好心人  让我用下电话吧
And the use of your phone, if you'd be so kind.

12:36.480 --> 12:40.810
别担心  只打个市内电话而已
Don't worry, it's a local call.

12:41.550 --> 12:45.370
我回家第一件事就是换条干净的内裤
First thing I do, we get home: Clean underwear.

12:45.380 --> 12:46.400
然后呢?
Then what?

12:46.410 --> 12:47.470
可能会回那个便利店
I guess go back to that liquor store

12:47.480 --> 12:51.180
求他们让我继续干下去
beg for my job back.

12:54.380 --> 12:55.740
我们曾有过机会
We had it.

12:55.750 --> 12:57.940
可惜擦肩而过
We were so close.

12:57.950 --> 13:01.740
我甚至还能依稀闻到那钱的味道
I can still taste that money right there in the back of my throat.

13:01.750 --> 13:03.100
我现在不考虑别的
Well, nothing that a couple of Keystones

13:03.110 --> 13:04.800
只想美美地吃上一顿汉堡肉饼
a hungry man salisbury steak dinner

13:04.810 --> 13:09.410
然后坐在电视机前看看电视
and a night in front of the TV won't take care of.

13:10.350 --> 13:14.040
嘿  妈妈  是我
Hey, mom, it's Brad.

13:14.050 --> 13:18.500
我和罗伊的车子出了点问题
Hey, listen, me and Roy, we ran into some car trouble and...

13:18.510 --> 13:20.600
你能否来接我们
we were wondering if you could come pick us up.

13:20.610 --> 13:22.240
不知道  等一下
I don't know, hold on.

13:22.250 --> 13:23.900
这该死的小镇叫什么?
What the hell town is this?

13:23.910 --> 13:26.440
你不是说仅打个市内电话吗
Thought you said this was a local call.

13:26.450 --> 13:28.570
嘿  布拉德利  看看这个
Hey, Bradley, check this out.

13:28.580 --> 13:29.740
别挂  妈妈
Wait, mom.

13:29.750 --> 13:32.070
