by the look of these pediatric meds

40:13.750 --> 40:16.570
随后四年他像打格陵兰海豹一样地打你
he beats you like a harp seal for the next four years.

40:16.580 --> 40:19.100
很大的打击  穷困  虐待儿童   别无选择
Big shock-- poor, abused kid, not a lot of options

40:19.110 --> 40:21.570
他参军了
he joins the military.

40:21.580 --> 40:24.100
有什么想问就开门见山吧 别在那喋喋不休
Will there be any actual questions, or is this just a show-and-tell?

40:24.110 --> 40:25.300
好  我有个问题
Okay, I got one.

40:25.310 --> 40:27.370
为什么一个普通的步兵
How does a guy go from infantry grunt

40:27.380 --> 40:31.200
作为特别观察员在第一次海湾战争表现平平
with less than stellar marks to the gulf 1, special ops,

40:31.210 --> 40:32.900
却能加入联邦调查局
to the federal bureau of investigations

40:32.910 --> 40:37.270
而且正领导着这个国家 有史以来最大的追捕行动?
leading the largest manhunt this country's ever seen?

40:37.280 --> 40:38.500
我有这些零星线索
I have all these dots.

40:38.510 --> 40:41.170
但是我却不能连系在一起
And there's just no way to connect them.

40:41.180 --> 40:44.640
你应该查你职权范围内的事情... 迪克
Looks like you need to work on your clearance level...Dick.

40:44.650 --> 40:46.200
或许我就想查你
Or maybe I just work on you.

40:46.210 --> 40:48.670
-你想这么做? -我要把你锁在这张桌子上
-You want to do this? -I will chain you to this desk

40:48.680 --> 40:50.940
直到我发现我的猜测是错误的
until I get some answers I cannot fertilize my lawn with.

40:50.950 --> 40:52.900
你确定你真的要这么做?
You sure you want to do this?

40:52.910 --> 40:55.200
我知道他们让你在国外做了什么  亚历克斯
I know what they tell you to do overseas, Alex,

40:55.210 --> 40:57.370
让我把话再说得更清楚点
and let me make it perfectly clear

40:57.380 --> 40:59.700
在美国国土上我们不能那样做
we do not do it on American soil.

40:59.710 --> 41:02.600
长官  有电话找你
Sir, uh, there's a phone call for you.

41:02.610 --> 41:04.000
我等一下再接
I'll take it later.

41:04.010 --> 41:08.550
长官  你最好现在就接
Uh, sir, you're gonna want to take this now.

41:11.850 --> 41:14.600
喂
Yeah.

41:14.610 --> 41:16.470
是  长官
Yes, sir.

41:16.480 --> 41:18.100
我...
I, uh...

41:18.110 --> 41:20.270
我现在就和他在一起
I'm with him now.

41:20.280 --> 41:23.070
是 长官
Yes, sir.

41:23.080 --> 41:25.210
好
Okay.

41:29.010 --> 41:30.540
你去哪儿?
Where you going, Rick?

41:30.550 --> 41:34.240
我想我们应该进入正题了
I thought we were really starting to get somewhere.

41:34.250 --> 41:38.410
我们走
Let's go.

41:51.550 --> 41:53.700
亚历克斯
Alex.

41:53.710 --> 41:58.750
你有什么给我?
You got something for me?

42:01.010 --> 42:03.940
打开它
open it.

42:03.950 --> 42:06.470
这些数字联系到
The numbers correlate

42:06.480 --> 42:08.340
手机上的字母
to the letters on a phone.

42:08.350 --> 42:09.800
只有这个可能
Only on this one

42:09.810 --> 42:12.500
其他组合都说不通
none of the possible combinations make sense.

42:12.510 --> 42:13.640
我们认为这数字对应的是个地点
We think it's a location

42:13.650 --> 42:14.870
迈克尔 斯科菲尔德约定的见面地点
a rendezvous point for Michael Scofield.

42:14.880 --> 42:16.000
找到了地点
You find it

42:16.010 --> 42:17.770
就找到了他
you find him.

42:17.780 --> 42:19.700
你该快些把我从那里弄出去
You know, you could have gotten me out of there sooner.

42:19.710 --> 42:22.370
我们需要通过些渠道
You know, even we have to go through certain channels

42:22.380 --> 42:25.300
才能把事情做得看起来可信
to make things appear on the up-and-up.

42:25.310 --> 42:27.970
亚历克斯你明白这些  不是吗?
You know all about that, don't you, Alex?

42:27.980 --> 42:32.450
保持原样吧
Keeping up appearances.

42:32.650 --> 42:34.000
很好
Good.

42:34.010 --> 42:36.800
我只是想确认一下
I was just making sure

42:36.810 --> 42:40.300
你是否还记得这次追捕的目标
that we're still clear on the directive of this manhunt.

42:40.310 --> 42:43.540
我知道...追捕布伦斯和斯科菲尔德的原因
You know, I understand the, uh, reasoning behind Burrows and Scofield,

42:43.550 --> 42:45.740
但是其他人...虽然他们可能是罪犯
but these other men-- criminals that they may be--

42:45.750 --> 42:48.370
但是没有证据表明...
there's nothing in their profiles to suggest...

42:48.380 --> 42:50.800
你只是被雇佣做事的
you've been hired to do a job.

42:50.810 --> 42:54.100
理由不关你的事
The reasoning does not concern you.

42:54.110 --> 42:56.140
不要问关于我们的问题
Don't ask any questions about us

42:56.150 --> 42:58.270
这样或许我们能继续保证不再有人调查你
and maybe we'll continue to make sure no one asks any questions about you.

42:58.280 --> 43:01.410
明白了吗?
Are we clear?

43:04.310 --> 43:08.180
全部都得死
They all die.
